_sText:
This map was made more so for experimentation with things than looks. I wanted to incorporate both the hostage and bomb maps together, and this is what I came up with. There are secret places throughout the map (3 to be exact). Including a room that is locked with a secret code. 

I would love to re-texture or have this map re-textured by someone else in the future as well as fixing other little things in the map as well as the lighting.
